result.adr_address: 39 Yin Chong St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 39 Yin Chong St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Ocio

reviews.text: The food is very tasty and comes in big portions. Good price/quality relation

First time trying today. The menu looked promising with reasonable prices.

My girlfriend ordered the lobster fettuccini. The pasta itself was decent. The lobster was about the size of a crawfish and only half of it. The meat was dry and quite tasteless, possibly overcooked.

I tried the lamb chops with mash. The lamb was also quite dry but tasted ok, not great. The portion of mash was VERY small.

We had to ask for napkins as they weren't provided on the table.

We were both quite hungry and as the portions were small we had to go somewhere else to buy more food.

My recommendations are to make sure the sides, like mash or fettuccini, are served in decent portions to make a full meal. The portion of lamb was OK, but the lobster was way to small for a full meal. Also review the way you cook your meat - it is way overcooked which results in less taste and dry meat.

Intimate western cafe that specialised in waffles. Brunch/lunch sets you off at about HKD80 to HKD90 with soup, main and a drink.

Generally the quality of the food is acceptable. Soup was slightly blend, the patty of the burger is a little overdone and overseasoned. We quite like the waffle though. Fried are crispy.

Friendly service and we enjoyed our meal.
Small western style restaurant. Acceptable food quality.
Worst steak ever…

result.adr_address: 香港旺角煙廠街39號
result.name: Ocio

reviews.text:
一直想搵一些平靚正dinner set：一個寧靜舒適嘅環境，可以同朋友促膝詳談。簡單three course就夠，如果有扒扒鋸就最好，不然的話有意粉都OK。價錢最好$200內。地點最好係油尖旺，方便大家。

今日比我搵到一間，喺旺角煙廠街。

餐廳名叫”OCIO”，牌匾寫的是撩草，好似高級嘅西餐廳般的。一邊環境都唔錯，樓底都幾高，座位之間有足夠空間，簡單優雅。

共有19款dinner set 可選，由$89到$178不等。有牛扒、春雞、意粉、漢堡、全日早餐等等。當中也有很多龍蝦的options，想到菜單上嘅照片，龍蝦都是原隻上，抵食。

【奧斯特選早餐】
全日早餐很豐富，有煙三文魚、雞扒、很長很長的薯仔及香腸、雞蛋、焗豆、窩夫及沙律菜等等。配有糖漿，淋上窩夫上食。
見到咁豐富的早餐，未食已經很興奮。

【奧斯BBQ醬春雞伴意粉】
有半隻春雞，伴有意粉及沙律菜。
春雞烤得剛剛好，雞肉多汁鮮嫩。值得一提的是，意粉煮得很有水準，應該是煮的時間控制得好好，不會太軟。調味到位，又夠熱，不是快餐廳的hea 意粉。

【奧斯水城雞翼】
+$39有5隻雞翼，夠多醬好滋味。

飲品方面我叫一個熱飲及凍牛奶，茶包是選用較貴的Twinings，贊！
試咗全日早午餐，如以價錢來說，食物份量太多，反而用多一些靚啲而量小啲的食材取代“量”比較好些。
甜品味道佳，份量足，但略嫌價錢太貴
伯爵茶hotcake很好吃，如果想吃梳乎厘班戟類的甜品，這裡的CP值很高。咖啡略遜色。
味幾好，不過麵粉類太多，蛋糕似麵包多啲，用Pan裝食物有好幾款，個Pan柄會熱傷人但店方無防護無警告無出聲，各位要小心。
